package.json added 6 deps (cytoscape, cytoscape-dagre, @types/cytoscape,
@nangohq/frontend, @nangohq/node, server-only) without regenerating the
lockfile. Vercel CI installs with --frozen-lockfile, so every production
build was failing at the install step (ERR_PNPM_OUTDATED_LOCKFILE) before
compiling. Regenerated the lockfile; frozen install now passes.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
